extendedInfo.description: Natural wondersFeatures:-Set images as wallpaper-Save images to sdcard (memory card)They say Mother Nature is the greatest artist of all and these magical landscapes out of this world are a proof that these words are true. Meet the greatest wonders of nature that will take your breath away: the fluorescent beach in Japan, stunning northern lights or aurora borealis effect, the worlds largest natural mirror, magical mountains in China that were the inspiration for the floating peaks of the movies Pandora, mysterious Devils Tower and other breathtaking natural wonders. All these magnificent natural wonders as wallpapers for your phone and for your viewing pleasure. No Photoshop, no special effects just pure nature at its best.
